---
source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Set the download directory

Usage: bl download dir [OPTIONS] <path>

Arguments:
  <path>  Directory to save downloads into

Options:
      --headless  Hide browser window (visible by default)
  -v, --verbose   Enable debug logging
      --json      Output as JSON
  -h, --help      Print help

Examples:
  bl download dir ./downloads
  # Set download directory to ./downloads
